    <note>Xue(1) Zhongru [7108] Adopted by Kui [803], his father's younger brother. Cousin and brother by adoption of Ouyang(1) Xiu's [1384] wife. Li(2) Zongyong's [1101] son-in-law. His daughter married Gao(1) Shijian [3449], a great grandson of Gao(1) Qiong [3441], who was the father of Gao(1) Jizhong [905], Gao(1) Jixuan [7113] and Gao(1) Jixun [3442]. She was the mother of Gao(1) Gongxuan [912] and probably either the grandmother or grandaunt of Gao(1) Shiding [921]. She was buried in Jizhou, Luling xian. Liu Caishao, 12.20a; SHY:ZG, 65.23b. CBD, 5, 4191.</note>
